reviewText: the description of the tapes was inaccurate. there were a few actual vhs tapes that were in ok condition and three dubbed copies of the workout tapes.

This is a complete program for those interested in fitness and health.  If you are looking for a "fad" type of program this program is not for you.  If you are fitness junky looking for another very long, extremely complicated, and intricatly choreographed program, it would be best if you looked elsewhere.  Gilad is a great instructor with awesome credentials.  I would venture to say he brings the "whole shootin' match" to the table!  If you are interested in fitness and health this is the one for you.
